{"tid":1930582,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[因DDoS推唔到再開過]請全面抵制黃金/188 金源及寶源代理行貨遊戲及主機","createTime":"2020-03-17T15:46:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T04:11:17.000Z","uid":1089,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"ce1be8ee81caa2f6a6c55341f25c17afe5042954","tid":1930582,"uid":1089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T15:46:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dGN7TuG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdGN7TuG.png&h=8c3c7a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/ncrbttnG/jj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FncrbttnG%2Fjj.png&h=9eb0eff4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你地覺得精品唔覺意share左撐狗已經夠仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁請你地睇下呢間大仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n抵制方法可以直接購入日版／歐美水貨或者eshop/PSN download<br />\n<br />\n接下來佢代理既大作係FIFA20, 預計9月24日／27日推出實體行貨<br />\n呢隻我諗GAME鋪已經order左大量貨，如果唔想玩死良心GAME鋪既可以買埋呢隻行貨先實行抵制行動，然後就要向相熟GAME鋪放風話比佢地知香港將會有一班玩家會長期罷買寶源代理既遊戲同主機，咁佢地自然就會識做入返日版水貨／歐美水貨返黎賣<br />\n<br />\n至於FIFA20之後最大tittle應該就係Pokemon 劍盾，根據上年比卡超／伊貝，日版係同樣支援正體中文，而且封面唔會寫住「精靈寶可夢」呢個支那譯名，所以要點買相信唔使多講<br />\n<br />\n行動目的只有一個，就係要各大廠商撤換香港代理，所以可以的話，請透過不同渠道／語言向日本／歐美廠商說明，或者集體SEND投訴信去香港／亞洲區總公司要求撤換代理商<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">抵制狗源，由劍盾做起</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">有關其他購買方法請參考</span><br />\n[Switch / PS4] 黃藍黑Game舖大集合<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1686000\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1686000</a><br />\n<br />\n或者直接從AEON, Apita/UNY, Fortress都可買到由任天堂(香港)直接供貨既行貨<br />\n<br />\n亦可以通過各種外國購買網站購入水貨(e.g. <a href=\"http://amazon.co.jp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Famazon.co.jp&d=Ih%2BYJd3WmO0qFhbj2imzB258GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=39adcb1e\" target=\"_blank\">amazon.co.jp</a>)"},{"pid":"ca084cd0da530e69f3d5613e83b4a92b2f607205","tid":1930582,"uid":1089,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T15:48:19.000Z","msg":"適逢動物之森發售日<br />\n狗源唔係以為我會忘記你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4148be7bea8f8deef46f68ef38988a3583e558a","tid":1930582,"uid":1089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T15:49:56.000Z","msg":"中文封面＋偷跑=100%狗源貨<br />\n<br />\n請購買前回想下香港警察過去大半年所作所為<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcf0aa8e9ed5c37f4f0291b3c24f156e9592e052","tid":1930582,"uid":1089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T15:51:27.000Z","msg":"DDoS又如何，POST照推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f1b2efa09a802af75204c64b1a5d1f588b8f98","tid":1930582,"uid":1089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T15:56:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2271a1624e3c0ae2d8dacd954a25eeda7bd3d275","tid":1930582,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T15:58:54.000Z","msg":"無幫襯好耐喇，藍撚到咁"},{"pid":"6d2812f6fbf52f96a0f6642574d60c89b6dfa6f6","tid":1930582,"uid":1089,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T16:04:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05744de40848da9f00e20cc7da9a79fee3d94f4c","tid":1930582,"uid":1089,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T16:15:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d58572eee10d69c56461f20d17af89967611d38","tid":1930582